nodes.text: Wes was a human male soldier for the Alliance to Restore the Republic. During the Galactic Civil War between the Alliance and the Galactic Empire, he fought Imperial troops on the moon Jedha.
Wes was a human male who joined the Alliance to Restore the Republic sometime during or before the year 0 BBY.
Wes was a human with gray eyes and fair skin.
Wes wore the fatigues of a Rebel trooper.
Wes was created as a playable character for the online browser video game Star Wars: Boots on the Ground. Players could select Wes to be a member of their three-man rebel squad.
